## üìÇ Project Structure
- `Ball.java` ‚Äì Ball physics and properties.  
- `Goal.java` ‚Äì Target hole representation.  
- `Physics.java` ‚Äì Physics engine and motion dynamics.  
- `ODESolvers.java` ‚Äì Numerical solvers for motion equations.  
- `Launch.java` ‚Äì Handles initial launch parameters.  
- `ManhattanBot.java` ‚Äì Custom Manhattan optimization bot.  
- `NewtonBot.java` ‚Äì Newton‚ÄìRaphson optimization bot.  

